Phobia still thought he was being pushed into making leadership decisions
even with KitKat restored to full health. He checked his weapons, his
scanners, and his basic mechanizms. he was ready. he exited the ship and
aproached his leader.  KitKat,  , we can begin tracking Megatron whenever
you're ready." he was proud of himself, he'd taken a bunch of rag tag troops
and escaped with only two losses.
